data.description: You won't want to miss this incredible Normandy home! Fabulous & open floorplan with rounded arches and amazing natural light! Tall 12' ceilings with spiral staircase greets you. Stunning wall of windows & architectural frosted block windows brighten the space. The kitchen offers a grand granite island, gas range, pots & pans drawers & glass tile backsplash for a modern look & feel. Office at the front of the home features french doors & is hard wired for internet. 1st floor primary suite offers walk-in closet, superb walk-in shower with controls & windows for more natural light. Dramatic staircase leads to second living area, 3 add'l beds & media room wired for 5.1 surround sound with its own (20 Amp) circuit breaker for high end audio capabilities. Other upgrades include radiant barrier, extra insulation in attic, gas tankless water heater, low thermal windows, dual NEST thermostats, wrapped construction technology underneath the brick layer and a separate foundation irrigation line.
